#FDA Advisory Comm (N=21) vote on if benefits of #COVID19 #vaccine outweigh risks for ages 16+ for initial emergency use auth:

17 Yes
4 No
1 Abstain

One member said pre-vote he wanted to vote yes, but only for age 18+, not 16+. No post-vote discussion of reason for no/abstain. https://t.co/ydOmFQsoAK
